<item>
            <title>[LU-15493] facet_failover () and wait_clients_import_state() improvements</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15493</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch contains the following proposed fixes and improvements:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fix template matching in affected facets accounting (when the == and != operators are used, the string to the right of the operator is considered a pattern);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reduce failover duration done by facet_failover(): Long failover duration needs increasing of ldlm_enqueue_min to avoid evictions with striped objects, so let&apos;s do node reboot and mount on failover node in parallel.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Make wait_clients_import_state() working with a facet list;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
